'''飓风迪安'''（{{lang-en|Hurricane Dean}}）是[[2007年大西洋飓风季|2007年大西洋飓风季]]最强烈的[[热带气旋|热带气旋]]，也是自[[2005年大西洋飓风季|2005年]]的[[飓风威尔玛|飓风威尔玛]]以来最强烈的[[北大西洋热带气旋|北大西洋飓风]]，在有纪录以来所有大西洋飓风中也可以排到第七位，还能在所有[[登陆_(气象学)|登陆]]过的大西洋飓风中排名第三。这股[[佛得角型飓风|佛得角型飓风]]于2007年8月13日形成，从[[大西洋|大西洋]]东部向西北偏西方向穿越[[圣卢西亚海峡|圣卢西亚海峡]]进入[[加勒比海|加勒比海]]。系统接下来逐渐增强成[[萨菲尔-辛普森飓风等级|大型飓风]]，并在8月20日从[[牙买加|牙买加]]南部近海经过前不久达到[[萨菲尔-辛普森飓风等级|萨菲尔-辛普森飓风等级]]下的五级飓风强度。8月21日，迪安以强劲的五级风暴强度在[[尤卡坦半岛|尤卡坦半岛]]登陆，穿越半岛进入[[坎佩切湾|坎佩切湾]]后虽有大幅削弱，但仍然达到飓风强度。系统接下来又有小幅增强，于8月22日在[[韦拉克鲁斯州|韦拉克鲁斯州]]实现二度登陆。之后迪安朝西北方向漂移，逐渐减弱成残留[[低气压|低气压]]，最终在[[美国西南部|美国西南部]]上空消散。

这场飓风产生的狂风、巨浪、暴雨和[[风暴潮|风暴潮]]导致十个国家共计有至少45人死亡，经济损失估计达到16.6亿美元（2007年美元，相当于{{#time:Y}}年的{{Formatprice|{{Inflation|US|1660000000|2007}}}}美元）。最先受到其冲击的是[[小安的列斯群岛|小安的列斯群岛]]，迪安给途经加勒比地区的农作物造成毁灭性打击，特别是在[[马提尼克|马提尼克]]和[[牙买加|牙买加]]。风暴在朝[[墨西哥|墨西哥]]逼近的过程中仍然有五级飓风强度，但幸运的是没有袭击人口稠密的地区，结果迪安登陆时虽然强度远高于途经加勒比地区岛屿的二级，但造成的破坏程度却要小得多，而且也没有导致任何人员丧生。

受影响地区的清理和重建工作花费数月时间才完成。多个国际救援组织筹集资金，与国有基金一起对道路清理、房屋重建和被毁农作物补植提供援助。受破坏最为严重的牙买加在之后超过一年的时间里也未能恢复风暴来袭前的[[香蕉|香蕉]]产量。墨西哥的[[旅游业|旅游业]]也是如此，花费近一年的时间重建受损的[[游船|游船]][[基础设施|基础设施]]。

迪安是继[[飓风安德鲁|飓风安德鲁]]于1992年8月24日登陆以来大西洋盆地第一个在登陆时仍然有五级强度的飓风<ref name="td4disc33">{{cite web |author = Richard Pasch, Daniel Brown | date = 2007-08-21 | title = Hurricane Dean Discussion Thirty Three | publisher = National Hurricane Center | accessdate = 2014-03-13 | archivedate = 2014-03-12 | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20140312213225/http://www.nhc.noaa.gov/archive/2007/al04/al042007.discus.033.shtml | deadurl = no | url = http://www.nhc.noaa.gov/archive/2007/al04/al042007.discus.033.shtml?}}</ref>，不过由于登陆区域地广人稀，因此其规模虽然比安德鲁大得多，但造成的破坏却远远不及。尽管如此，这场飓风仍然造成大范围且持久的破坏，[[世界气象组织|世界气象组织]]因此将其名称予以退役，今后都不会再在大西洋风暴命名中使用。

== 气象历史 ==
{{storm path|Dean 2007 track.png}}
{{main|飓风迪安的气象历史}}
2007年8月11日，一股强烈的东风波离开西非海岸<ref name="TWOAT081111">{{cite report | author = Richard Knabb | date = 2007-08-11 | title = August 11 Tropical Weather Outlook (1130) | publisher = National Hurricane Center | accessdate = 2007-08-14}}</ref>，由于外界环境有利<ref name="TWOAT07081205">{{cite report | author = Jamie Rhome | date = 2007-08-12 | title = August 12 Tropical Weather Outlook (0530) | publisher = National Hurricane Center | accessdate = 2007-08-14}}</ref>，东风波逐渐获得发展，于8月13日在[[佛得角|佛得角]][[罗盘方位|西南偏西方向]]约835公里洋面成为[[热带气旋|热带低气压]]，[[国家飓风中心|美国国家飓风中心]]将其归类为“第四号热带低气压”<ref name="TWOAT07081311">{{cite report | author = Richard Knabb, Eric Blake | date = 2007-08-13 |title=August 13 Tropical Weather Outlook (1130) | publisher = National Hurricane Center | accessdate = 2007-08-14}}</ref>。低气压快速西进<ref name="td4disc3">{{cite web |author=Daniel Brown, James Franklin |date=2007-08-13 |title=Tropical Depression Four Discussion Three |work=National Hurricane Center |publisher=National Oceanic and Atmospheric Administration |accessdate=2014-03-07 |archiveurl= https://web.archive.org/web/20140103034602/http://www.nhc.noaa.gov/archive/2007/al04/al042007.discus.003.shtml |archivedate=2014-01-03 |deadurl=no |url=http://www.nhc.noaa.gov/archive/2007/al04/al042007.discus.003.shtml?}}</ref>，于[[协调世界时|协调世界时]]8月14日下午15点达到热带风暴强度，美国国家飓风中心因此将其命名为“迪安”（{{lang|en|Dean}}）<ref name="td4disc5">{{cite web |author = Lixion Avila |date=2007-08-15 |title=Tropical Storm Dean Discussion Five |work=National Hurricane Center |publisher=National Oceanic and Atmospheric Administration |url=http://www.nhc.noaa.gov/archive/2007/al04/al042007.discus.005.shtml? |deadurl=no |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20140103021520/http://www.nhc.noaa.gov/archive/2007/al04/al042007.discus.005.shtml |accessdate=2014-03-07 |archivedate=2014-01-03}}</ref>。风暴继续增强<ref name="td4disc7">{{cite web | author = Daniel Brown | date = 2007-08-14 | title = Tropical Storm Dean Discussion Seven | publisher = National Hurricane Center | archivedate = 2014-03-09 | deadurl = no | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20140309113748/http://www.nhc.noaa.gov/archive/2007/al04/al042007.discus.007.shtml | accessdate = 2014-03-12 | url = http://www.nhc.noaa.gov/archive/2007/al04/al042007.discus.007.shtml?}}</ref>，不过其北面存在的干冷空气延缓了结构发展。8月15日，系统中有[[雨带|不规则的雨带]]形成<ref name="td4disc8">{{cite web |author = Jack Beven | date = 2007-08-15 | title = Tropical Storm Dean Discussion Eight | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20140103024247/http://www.nhc.noaa.gov/archive/2007/al04/al042007.discus.008.shtml | work = National Hurricane Center | publisher = National Oceanic and Atmospheric Administration |accessdate=2014-03-07 |url=http://www.nhc.noaa.gov/archive/2007/al04/al042007.discus.008.shtml? |archivedate=2014-01-03 |deadurl=no}}</ref>，到当天夜间已经形成部分[[风眼|风眼墙]]<ref name="td4disc10">{{cite web | author = Eric Blake | date = 2007-08-15 | title = Tropical Storm Dean Discussion Ten | publisher = National Hurricane Center | accessdate = 2014-03-12 | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20140309113514/http://www.nhc.noaa.gov/archive/2007/al04/al042007.discus.010.shtml | url = http://www.nhc.noaa.gov/archive/2007/al04/al042007.discus.010.shtml? | archivedate = 2014-03-09 | deadurl = no}}</ref>。
[[File:Dean_18_aug_2007_1409Z.jpg|thumb]]]]

风暴继续增强<ref name="td4disc11">{{cite web | author = Daniel Brown | date = 2007-08-15 | title = Tropical Storm Dean Discussion Eleven | publisher = National Hurricane Center | accessdate = 2014-03-12 | archivedate = 2014-03-09 | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20140309113544/http://www.nhc.noaa.gov/archive/2007/al04/al042007.discus.011.shtml | deadurl = no | url = http://www.nhc.noaa.gov/archive/2007/al04/al042007.discus.011.shtml?}}</ref>，美国国家飓风中心于[[协调世界时|UTC]]8月16日上午9点将迪安升级为飓风<ref name="td4disc12">{{cite web | author = Jack Beven | date = 2007-08-16 | title = Hurricane Dean Discussion Twelve | work = National Hurricane Center | publisher = National Oceanic and Atmospheric Administration | accessdate = 2014-03-07 | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20140103010432/http://www.nhc.noaa.gov/archive/2007/al04/al042007.discus.012.shtml |archivedate=2014-01-03 |url=http://www.nhc.noaa.gov/archive/2007/al04/al042007.discus.012.shtml? | deadurl = no}}</ref>。北面强烈的[[高压脊|高压脊]]迫使迪安继续向西面的加勒比海行进<ref name="td4disc13">{{cite web |author=Eric Blake |date=2007-08-16 |title=Hurricane Dean Discussion Thirteen |work=National Hurricane Center |publisher=National Oceanic and Atmospheric Administration |accessdate=2014-03-07 |archivedate=2014-01-03 |deadurl=no |archiveurl= https://web.archive.org/web/20140103034923/http://www.nhc.noaa.gov/archive/2007/al04/al042007.discus.013.shtml |url=http://www.nhc.noaa.gov/archive/2007/al04/al042007.discus.013.shtml?}}</ref>，风暴很快增强成二级飓风<ref name="td4disc14">{{cite web |author=Lixion Avila, Eric Blake |date=2007-08-16 |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20140103033231/http://www.nhc.noaa.gov/archive/2007/al04/al042007.discus.014.shtml |title=Hurricane Dean Discussion Fourteen |work=National Hurricane Center |publisher=National Oceanic and Atmospheric Administration |accessdate=2014-03-07 |url=http://www.nhc.noaa.gov/archive/2007/al04/al042007.discus.014.shtml? |deadurl=no |archivedate=2014-01-03}}</ref><ref name="td4disc15">{{cite web |author=James Franklin |date=2007-08-16 |title=Hurricane Dean Discussion Fifteen |archiveurl= https://web.archive.org/web/20140103022029/http://www.nhc.noaa.gov/archive/2007/al04/al042007.discus.015.shtml |work=National Hurricane Center |publisher=National Oceanic and Atmospheric Administration | accessdate = 2014-03-13 | url = http://www.nhc.noaa.gov/archive/2007/al04/al042007.discus.015.shtml? | archivedate = 2014-01-03 | deadurl = no}}</ref>。接下来风暴的发展略有减缓<ref name="td4disc16">{{cite web | author = Jack Beven | date = 2007-08-17 | title = Hurricane Dean Discussion Sixteen | work = National Hurricane Center | publisher = National Oceanic and Atmospheric Administration | accessdate = 2014-03-07 | url = http://www.nhc.noaa.gov/archive/2007/al04/al042007.discus.016.shtml? | archivedate = 2014-01-03 |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20140103033834/http://www.nhc.noaa.gov/archive/2007/al04/al042007.discus.016.shtml |deadurl=no}}</ref>，但8月17日途经小安的列斯群岛期间一架[[飓风猎人|飓风猎人]][[侦察机|侦察机]]发现风眼墙已经闭合，形成清晰的[[风眼|风眼]]<ref name="td4disc17">{{cite web | author = Lixion Avila | date = 2007-08-17 | title = Hurricane Dean Discussion Seventeen | work = National Hurricane Center | publisher = National Oceanic and Atmospheric Administration | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20140103014244/http://www.nhc.noaa.gov/archive/2007/al04/al042007.discus.017.shtml | accessdate = 2014-03-07 |url = http://www.nhc.noaa.gov/archive/2007/al04/al042007.discus.017.shtml? | archivedate = 2014-01-03}}</ref>。侦察机测得的数据还表明迪安已经增强到三级飓风强度，成为大型飓风<ref name="td4disc18">{{cite web | author = Lixion Avila, Michelle Mainelli | date = 2007-08-17 | title = Hurricane Dean Discussion Eighteen | work = National Hurricane Center | deadurl = no | publisher = National Oceanic and Atmospheric Administration | accessdate = 2014-03-07 | archivedate = 2014-01-03 | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20140103023600/http://www.nhc.noaa.gov/archive/2007/al04/al042007.discus.018.shtml |url=http://www.nhc.noaa.gov/archive/2007/al04/al042007.discus.018.shtml?}}</ref>，系统的许多弧形气旋对流带仍然保持在小安的列斯群岛上空<ref name="td4disc19">{{cite web | author = Lixion Avila | date = 2007-08-17 | title = Hurricane Dean Special Discussion Nineteen | work = National Hurricane Center | publisher = National Oceanic and Atmospheric Administration | accessdate = 2014-03-07 | archivedate = 2014-01-03 | deadurl = no | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20140103025504/http://www.nhc.noaa.gov/archive/2007/al04/al042007.discus.019.shtml |url=http://www.nhc.noaa.gov/archive/2007/al04/al042007.discus.019.shtml?}}</ref>。8月17日晚，另一架对迪安执行侦察任务的飓风猎人发现风暴已经达到四级飓风强度<ref name="td4disc19a">{{cite web | author = Richard Knabb | date = 2007-08-17 | title = Hurricane Dean Intermediate Advisory Nineteen 'A' |work=National Hurricane Center |deadurl=no |publisher=National Oceanic and Atmospheric Administration |accessdate=2007-08-17 |archivedate=2014-01-02 |archiveurl= https://web.archive.org/web/20140102220433/http://www.nhc.noaa.gov/archive/2007/al04/al042007.public_a.019.shtml |url=http://www.nhc.noaa.gov/archive/2007/al04/al042007.public_a.019.shtml?}}</ref>，并且夜间其强度和规模都还在继续增大<ref name="td4disc20">{{cite web |author=Richard Knabb |date=2007-08-17 |title=Hurricane Dean Discussion Twenty |work=National Hurricane Center |publisher=National Oceanic and Atmospheric Administration |accessdate=2014-03-07 |url=http://www.nhc.noaa.gov/archive/2007/al04/al042007.discus.020.shtml? |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20140103024026/http://www.nhc.noaa.gov/archive/2007/al04/al042007.discus.020.shtml |archivedate=2014-01-03 |deadurl=no}}</ref>。8月18日，飓风发展出双层风眼墙<ref name="td4disc23">{{cite web |author=Lixion Avila |date=2007-08-18 |title=Hurricane Dean Discussion Twenty Three |work=National Hurricane Center |publisher=National Oceanic and Atmospheric Administration |accessdate=2014-03-07 |url=http://www.nhc.noaa.gov/archive/2007/al04/al042007.discus.023.shtml? |archivedate=2014-01-03 |archiveurl= https://web.archive.org/web/20140103035720/http://www.nhc.noaa.gov/archive/2007/al04/al042007.discus.023.shtml |deadurl=no}}</ref>，表明迪安正在进行[[眼墙置换|眼墙置换]]周期，风暴因此减弱成四级飓风，强度上开始出现短期波动<ref name="td4disc22">{{cite web |author=Lixion Avila |date=2007-08-18 |title=Hurricane Dean Discussion Twenty Two |work=National Hurricane Center |publisher=National Oceanic and Atmospheric Administration |accessdate=2014-03-07 |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20140103011629/http://www.nhc.noaa.gov/archive/2007/al04/al042007.discus.022.shtml |archivedate=2014-01-03 |url=http://www.nhc.noaa.gov/archive/2007/al04/al042007.discus.022.shtml? |deadurl=no}}</ref>。当天下午，飓风的外流结构继续改善，众多的螺旋带也令其卫星图像非常清晰<ref name="td4disc23" />。气象部门在当时的实际操作中认为8月18日迪安的强度没有超过四级，但风暴过后的分析表明，飓风这天的[[最大持续风速|最大持续风速]]已经达到每小时265公里，成为五级飓风。8月19日清晨，完成眼墙置换周期的迪安强度只有小幅降低，并开始对牙买加产生影响<ref name="td4disc25">{{cite web | author = Richard Pasch, Daniel Brown |date=2007-08-19 |title=Hurricane Dean Discussion Twenty Five | work = National Hurricane Center |publisher=National Oceanic and Atmospheric Administration |accessdate=2014-03-07 |archiveurl= https://web.archive.org/web/20140103020325/http://www.nhc.noaa.gov/archive/2007/al04/al042007.discus.025.shtml |url=http://www.nhc.noaa.gov/archive/2007/al04/al042007.discus.025.shtml? |archivedate=2014-01-03 |deadurl=no}}</ref>。

8月19日晚，迪安在牙买加以南近海掠过<ref name="td4disc27">{{cite web | author = James Franklin, Jamie Rhome | date = 2007-08-19 | title = Hurricane Dean Discussion Twenty Seven | publisher = National Hurricane Center | accessdate = 2014-03-12 | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20140102210145/http://www.nhc.noaa.gov/archive/2007/al04/al042007.discus.027.shtml | url = http://www.nhc.noaa.gov/archive/2007/al04/al042007.discus.027.shtml? | archivedate = 2014-01-02 | deadurl = no}}</ref>，并在夜间开始再度增强<ref name="td4public28">{{cite web |author=Richard Knabb, Dave Roberts |title=Hurricane Dean Public Advisory Twenty Eight |work=National Hurricane Center |publisher=National Oceanic and Atmospheric Administration |url=http://www.nhc.noaa.gov/archive/2007/al04/al042007.public.028.shtml? |deadurl=no |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20140103014754/http://www.nhc.noaa.gov/archive/2007/al04/al042007.public.028.shtml |archivedate=2014-01-03 |accessdate=2014-03-07 |date=2007-08-19}}</ref>，系统中有紧密的单层风眼形成，表明已经完成的眼壁更换周期不但没有削弱，反而强化了风暴<ref name="td4disc28">{{cite web |author=Richard Knabb |date=2007-08-19 |title=Hurricane Dean Discussion Twenty Eight |work=National Hurricane Center |publisher=National Oceanic and Atmospheric Administration |accessdate=2014-03-07 |archivedate=2014-01-02 |deadurl=no |archiveurl= https://web.archive.org/web/20140102193046/http://www.nhc.noaa.gov/archive/2007/al04/al042007.discus.028.shtml |url=http://www.nhc.noaa.gov/archive/2007/al04/al042007.discus.028.shtml?}}</ref>。8月20日早上，风暴中再度出现同心风眼壁，但持续的时间很短。美国东南部上空的深层[[高气压|高压系统]]还在不断增强，迫使风暴向西北偏北方向移动，进入温度越来越高的水域并开始再度增强<ref name="td4disc29">{{cite web |author=Richard Pasch, Daniel Brown |date=2007-08-20 |title=Hurricane Dean Discussion Twenty Nine |work=National Hurricane Center |publisher=National Oceanic and Atmospheric Administration |accessdate=2014-03-08 |archiveurl= https://web.archive.org/web/20140102193030/http://www.nhc.noaa.gov/archive/2007/al04/al042007.discus.029.shtml |url=http://www.nhc.noaa.gov/archive/2007/al04/al042007.discus.029.shtml? |archivedate=2014-01-02 |deadurl=no}}</ref>。这天，风眼墙变得更加层次分明<ref name="td4disc30">{{cite web | author = James Franklin | date = 2007-08-20 | title = Hurricane Dean Discussion Thirty |work=National Hurricane Center |publisher=National Oceanic and Atmospheric Administration |accessdate=2014-03-08 |archivedate=2014-01-02 |deadurl=no |archiveurl= https://web.archive.org/web/20140102223211/http://www.nhc.noaa.gov/archive/2007/al04/al042007.discus.030.shtml |url=http://www.nhc.noaa.gov/archive/2007/al04/al042007.discus.030.shtml?}}</ref>，{{lang|en|UTC}}8月21日凌晨0点35分，迪安再度达到五级飓风强度<ref name="nhcupdate Cat5">{{cite web |author=Richard Knabb |date=2007-08-20 |title=Hurricane Dean Tropical Cyclone Update |work=National Hurricane Center |publisher=National Oceanic and Atmospheric Administration |accessdate=2014-03-08 |archivedate=2014-01-02 |archiveurl= https://web.archive.org/web/20140102193236/http://www.nhc.noaa.gov/archive/2007/al04/al042007.update.08210034.shtml |deadurl=no |url=http://www.nhc.noaa.gov/archive/2007/al04/al042007.update.08210034.shtml?}}</ref>。风暴以五级强度在位于墨西哥和[[伯利兹|伯利兹]]边界东北方向约65公里外，[[金塔纳罗奥州|金塔纳罗奥州]]的[[科斯塔玛雅|科斯塔玛雅]]（{{lang|en|Costa Maya}}）地区小镇玛哈瓦（{{lang|en|Majahual}}）附近登陆，并在进入陆地上空后迅速减弱，到风暴穿过尤卡坦半岛时已经削弱到只有一级飓风强度<ref>{{cite web | author = Staff Writer | publisher = Sky News | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20140103004653/http://news.sky.com/story/534465/mudslide-fears-after-dean-batters-mexico | archivedate = 2014-01-03 | deadurl = no | date = 2007-08-21 | accessdate = 2014-03-12 | url = http://news.sky.com/story/534465/mudslide-fears-after-dean-batters-mexico | title = Mudslide Fears After Dean Batters Mexico}}</ref><ref name="td4disc34">{{cite web |author=James Franklin |date=2007-08-21 |title=Hurricane Dean Discussion Thirty Four |work=National Hurricane Center |publisher=National Oceanic and Atmospheric Administration |accessdate=2014-03-08 |url=http://www.nhc.noaa.gov/archive/2007/al04/al042007.discus.034.shtml? |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20140103031433/http://www.nhc.noaa.gov/archive/2007/al04/al042007.discus.034.shtml |archivedate=2014-01-03 |deadurl=no}}</ref><ref name="td4public34a">{{cite web |author=James Franklin, Jamie Rhome |date=2007-08-21 |title=Hurricane Dean Intermediate Advisory Thirty Four A | work = National Hurricane Center |publisher=National Oceanic and Atmospheric Administration | accessdate = 2014-03-08 | archivedate = 2014-01-03 | deadurl = no | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20140103022031/http://www.nhc.noaa.gov/archive/2007/al04/al042007.public_a.034.shtml |url=http://www.nhc.noaa.gov/archive/2007/al04/al042007.public_a.034.shtml?}}</ref>。迪安在穿越墨西哥湾的过程中由于[[海面温度|海面温度]]较高而再度加强，于{{lang|en|UTC}}8月22日下午16点30分在韦拉克鲁斯州东海岸小镇[[特科卢特拉|特科卢特拉]]（{{lang|en|Tecolutla}}）附近实现第二次，也是最后一次登陆，登陆点位于[[图斯潘_(韦拉克鲁斯州)|图斯潘]]东南偏南方向约65公里，古蒂埃雷斯萨莫拉（{{lang|es|Gutiérrez Zamora}}）东侧，然后在向西行进的过程中迅速减弱，在数小时内就失去了下层环流，并于次日接触到[[东马德雷山脉|东马德雷山脉]]时失去中层环流。风暴残留经过该山脉，以一片广阔低气压区的形式进入东[[太平洋|太平洋]]<ref name="td4disc40">{{cite web |author=Lixion Avila |date=2007-08-22 |title=Hurricane Dean Discussion Forty |work=National Hurricane Center |publisher=National Oceanic and Atmospheric Administration |accessdate=2014-03-08 |archivedate=2014-01-02 |deadurl=no |archiveurl= https://web.archive.org/web/20140102193103/http://www.nhc.noaa.gov/archive/2007/al04/al042007.discus.040.shtml |url=http://www.nhc.noaa.gov/archive/2007/al04/al042007.discus.040.shtml?}}</ref>，最终围绕一个[[反气旋|反气旋]]向西北方向以大致平行于墨西哥海岸线的路径移动进入美国西南部<ref>{{cite report |author=Stuart Hinson |date=2007-08-26 |title=NCDC Event Record Details 679276 |work=National Climate Data Center |publisher=National Oceanic and Atmospheric Administration |accessdate=2008-07-02}}</ref>，于8月27日完全消散<ref>{{cite web | author = Jackson | date = 2007-08-30 | title = Surface Weather Map at 7:00 A.M. E.S.T. | work = National Centers for Environmental Prediction, Hydrometeorological Prediction Center | publisher = National Oceanic and Atmospheric Administration | accessdate = 2014-03-08 | archivedate = 2014-01-02 | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20140102193050/http://www.wpc.ncep.noaa.gov/dailywxmap/index_20070830.html | url = http://www.wpc.ncep.noaa.gov/dailywxmap/index_20070830.html | deadurl = no}}</ref>。

== 防灾措施 ==
飓风迪安的行进路径基本上没有变数，完全符合气象部门的预期，因此途经的所有国家都获得异常充分的警告，拥有充足的时间准备应对风暴的冲击<ref name="TCR">{{cite web | author = James Franklin | date = 2008-04-07 |title=Tropical Cyclone Report for Hurricane Dean | work = National Hurricane Center | publisher = National Oceanic and Atmospheric Administration | accessdate = 2014-03-12 | url = http://www.nhc.noaa.gov/pdf/TCR-AL042007_Dean.pdf | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20131012024447/http://www.nhc.noaa.gov/pdf/TCR-AL042007_Dean.pdf | format = PDF | archivedate = 2013-10-12 | deadurl = no}}</ref>。风暴极大的强度和气象部门的提前警告促使[[中美洲|中美洲]]和加勒比地区各国开设成百上千个避难所，数以千计的灾难恢复专家进入待命状态，数十万易受影响地区的居民及时撤离，还准备了数百万美元的紧急救援物资。

=== 小安的列斯群岛 ===
{| class="infobox" border="0" cellspacing="0" cellpadding="0" style="background:transparent;text-align:center; font-size:95%; width:12.6em; float:{{{align|right}}};" 
|-
|style="background-color:#{{Storm_colour|cat5}};" title=“估计将在36小时内受到飓风（风速至少达到每小时118公里）袭击”| '''[[热带气旋警告|飓风警告]]'''<br/><small>36小时内受飓风袭击</small>
|-
|style="background-color:#{{Storm_colour|cat4}};" title=“估计将在48小时内受到飓风（风速至少达到每小时118公里）袭击”| '''[[热带气旋警告|飓风观察预警]]'''<br/><small>48小时内受飓风袭击</small>
|-
|style="background-color:#{{Storm_colour|cat3}};" title="估计将在36小时内受到热带风暴（风速每小时63至117公里）袭击"| '''[[热带气旋警告|热带风暴警告]]'''<br/><small>36小时内受热带风暴袭击</small>
|-
|style="background-color:#{{Storm_colour|cat1}};" title=“估计将在48小时内受到热带风暴（风速每小时63至117公里）袭击”| '''[[热带气旋警告|热带风暴观察预警]]'''<br/><small>48小时内受热带风暴袭击</small>
|}
随着飓风迪安逼近小安的列斯群岛，当地气象部门发布[[热带气旋警告|热带气旋警告和观察预警]]，建议居民对风暴来袭做好准备。[[圣卢西亚|圣卢西亚]]、[[多米尼克|多米尼克]]<ref name="td4public12">{{cite web | author = Jack Beven | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20140103022243/http://www.nhc.noaa.gov/archive/2007/al04/al042007.public.012.shtml | date = 2007-08-16 | title = Hurricane Dean Public Advisory Twelve | publisher = National Hurricane Center | accessdate = 2014-03-12 | url = http://www.nhc.noaa.gov/archive/2007/al04/al042007.public.012.shtml? | archivedate = 2014-01-03 | deadurl = no}}</ref>、马提尼克、瓜德罗普岛及其附属地区收到飓风警告<ref name="td4public14">{{cite web | author = Lixion Avila, Eric Blake | date = 2007-08-16 | title = Hurricane Dean Public Advisory Fourteen | publisher = National Hurricane Center | accessdate = 2014-03-12 | url = http://www.nhc.noaa.gov/archive/2007/al04/al042007.public.014.shtml? | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20140103003437/http://www.nhc.noaa.gov/archive/2007/al04/al042007.public.014.shtml | archivedate = 2014-01-03 | deadurl = no}}</ref>。[[萨巴_(荷兰)|萨巴]]和[[圣尤斯特歇斯|圣尤斯特歇斯]]收到飓风观察预警<ref name="td4public11">{{cite web | author = Daniel Brown | date = 2007-08-15 | title = Tropical Storm Dean Public Advisory Eleven | publisher = National Hurricane Center | accessdate = 2014-03-12 | archivedate = 2014-01-03 | deadurl = no | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20140103001059/http://www.nhc.noaa.gov/archive/2007/al04/al042007.public.011.shtml | url = http://www.nhc.noaa.gov/archive/2007/al04/al042007.public.011.shtml?}}</ref>。[[巴巴多斯|巴巴多斯]]<ref name="td4update12b">{{cite web | author = Richard Pasch | date = 2007-08-16 | title = Hurricane Dean Tropical Cyclone Update | publisher = National Hurricane Center | accessdate = 2014-03-12 | archivedate = 2014-01-03 | deadurl = no | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20140103025244/http://www.nhc.noaa.gov/archive/2007/al04/al042007.update.08161239.shtml | url = http://www.nhc.noaa.gov/archive/2007/al04/al042007.update.08161239.shtml?}}</ref>、[[安地卡岛|安地卡岛]]、[[巴布达岛|巴布达岛]]、[[圣基茨岛|圣基茨岛]]、[[尼维斯|尼维斯]]、[[圣马丁岛_(加勒比海)|圣马丁岛]]<ref name="td4public13">{{cite web | author = Lixion Avila, Eric Blake | date = 2007-08-16 | title = Hurricane Dean Public Advisory Thirteen | publisher = National Hurricane Center | accessdate = 2014-03-12 | url = http://www.nhc.noaa.gov/archive/2007/al04/al042007.public.013.shtml? | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20140103033236/http://www.nhc.noaa.gov/archive/2007/al04/al042007.public.013.shtml | archivedate = 2014-01-03 | deadurl = no}}</ref>、[[圣文森特和格林纳丁斯|圣文森特和格林纳丁斯]]<ref name="td4public13" />、[[美属维尔京群岛|美属维尔京群岛]]<ref name="td4public15">{{cite web | author = James Franklin, Daniel Brown | date = 2007-08-16 | title = Hurricane Dean Public Advisory Fifteen | publisher = National Hurricane Center | accessdate = 2014-03-12 | archivedate = 2014-01-03 | deadurl = no | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20140102201911/http://www.nhc.noaa.gov/archive/2007/al04/al042007.public.015.shtml | url = http://www.nhc.noaa.gov/archive/2007/al04/al042007.public.015.shtml?}}</ref>和[[英属维尔京群岛|英属维尔京群岛]]都收到了热带风暴警告<ref name="td4public16">{{cite web | author = Jack Beven | date = 2007-08-17 | title = Hurricane Dean Public Advisory Sixteen | publisher = National Hurricane Center | accessdate = 2014-03-12 | archivedate = 2014-01-03 | deadurl = no | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20140103024459/http://www.nhc.noaa.gov/archive/2007/al04/al042007.public.016.shtml | url = http://www.nhc.noaa.gov/archive/2007/al04/al042007.public.016.shtml?}}</ref>。[[荷属圣马丁|荷属圣马丁]]<ref name="td4public11" />、[[圣文森特岛|圣文森特岛]]、[[格林纳达|格林纳达]]及其附属地区<ref name="td4update12b" />，[[蒙塞拉特岛|蒙塞拉特岛]]和[[安圭拉|安圭拉]]收到了热带风暴观察预警<ref name="td4public14a">{{cite web | author = James Franklin, Daniel Brown | date = 2007-08-16 | title = Hurricane Dean Public Advisory Fourteen A | publisher = National Hurricane Center | accessdate = 2007-08-16 | archivedate = 2014-01-03 | url = http://www.nhc.noaa.gov/archive/2007/al04/al042007.public_a.014.shtml? | deadurl = no | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20140103021257/http://www.nhc.noaa.gov/archive/2007/al04/al042007.public_a.014.shtml}}</ref>。

地方政府关闭多个[[机场|机场]]，开设多处避难所<ref name="IHT preps">{{cite web | title = Hurricane Dean strengthens as it takes aim at Caribbean islands | archivedate = 2014-03-12 |deadurl = no | date = 2007-08-15 | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20140312082018/http://savannahnow.com/michael-melia/2007-08-15/hurricane-dean-strengthens-it-takes-aim-caribbean-islands | accessdate = 2014-03-12 | author = Michael Melia | agency = Associated Press | url = http://savannahnow.com/michael-melia/2007-08-15/hurricane-dean-strengthens-it-takes-aim-caribbean-islands}}</ref>，还安排应急服务人员进入待命状态<ref name="BBC News August 17">{{cite news | author = Staff writer | date = 2007-08-17 | title = Hurricane hits eastern Caribbean | agency = BBC News | accessdate = 2007-08-17}}</ref>。马提尼克政府取消对[[西加勒比海航空708号班机空难|西加勒比海航空708号班机空难]]遇难者的纪念活动开始设立避难所<ref name="IHT preps" />。多明尼克安排游客疏散到混凝土掩体中，还把[[罗斯大学医学院|罗斯大学医学院]]的绝大多数外国医学生撤离该岛<ref name="IHT preps" />。多明尼克政府还取消紧急服务人员的休假<ref name="BBC News August 17" />，并疏散玛格丽特王妃医院，以防医院的屋顶被风暴破坏而给人员构成威胁<ref name="paho_2007-08-21">{{cite web | author = PAHO/WHO Caribbean Program Coordination | date = 2007-08-23 | accessdate = 2014-03-12 | publisher = Pan American Health Organization | archivedate = 2012-11-01 | title = Hurricane Dean in the Caribbean and Mexico, August 2007 | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20121101033808/http://www.paho.org/english/dd/ped/HurricaneDean807.htm | deadurl = yes | url = http://www1.paho.org/English/DD/PED/HurricaneDean807.htm }}</ref>。多明尼克的主机场和圣卢西亚的两个商用机场都在8月16日晚所有班机降落，迪安的外围[[雨带|雨带]]开始横扫该岛时关闭<ref name="wkrn_2007-08-17">{{cite web | author = Michael Melia | date = 2007-08-17 | title = Hurricane Takes Aim at Caribbean Islands | publisher = WashingtonPost.com | accessdate = 2014-03-12 |url=http://www.washingtonpost.com/wp-dyn/content/article/2007/08/16/AR2007081602951.html}}</ref>。

由于预料迪安会造成严重的破坏，多个应急响应团体开始筹集资金，安排人员进入待命状态。8月14日，加勒比灾害应急机构（{{lang|en|Caribbean Disaster Emergency Response Agency}}，简称{{lang|en|CDERA}}）启动地区响应机制，并联系小安的列斯群岛所有成员国的国家灾害协调人<ref name="CDERA_summary_2007-08-22">{{cite web | author = CDERA | publisher = Caribbean Disaster Emergency Response Agency | date = 2007-08-22 | accessdate = 2014-03-12 | title = Summary of Impact of Hurricane "Dean" on CDERA Participating States | format = PDF | archivedate = 2013-09-09 | url = http://reliefweb.int/sites/reliefweb.int/files/resources/E29328C01CE8F1C949257341000274B0-Full_Report.pdf | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20130909035731/http://reliefweb.int/sites/reliefweb.int/files/resources/E29328C01CE8F1C949257341000274B0-Full_Report.pdf}}</ref>。8月15日，[[美国国际开发署|美国国际开发署]]赶在飓风前派出多个工作组赶赴巴巴多斯、多明尼克和圣基茨，对风暴可能影响的地方做出损害评估<ref name="relief_web_USAID_2007-08-23">{{cite web | author = United States Agency for International Development (USAID) | publisher = Relief Web | date = 2007-08-23 | accessdate = 2014-03-12 | title = USAID provides hurricane assistance to Dominica and St. Lucia | archivedate = 2014-03-12 | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20140312092700/http://reliefweb.int/report/dominica/usaid-provides-hurricane-assistance-dominica-and-st-lucia | url = http://reliefweb.int/report/dominica/usaid-provides-hurricane-assistance-dominica-and-st-lucia | deadurl = no}}</ref>。东加勒比捐助小组于8月16日在[[联合国开发计划署|联合国开发计划署]]巴巴多斯居民代表主席召集下召开会议，对各成员国将会需要的国际援助做出预期<ref name="CDERA_summary_2007-08-22" />。

=== 大安的列斯群岛 ===
[[File:HurricaneDean.jpg|thumb]]从[[国际空间站|国际空间站]]上拍摄到的飓风迪安照片，中间的[[风眼|风眼]]清晰可见]]
牙买加全国<ref name="td4public22">{{cite web | author = Lixion Avila | title = Hurricane Dean Public Advisory Twenty Two | publisher = National Hurricane Center | accessdate = 2014-03-12 | date = 2007-08-18 | archivedate = 2014-01-02 | url = http://www.nhc.noaa.gov/archive/2007/al04/al042007.public.022.shtml? | deadurl = no | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20140102193542/http://www.nhc.noaa.gov/archive/2007/al04/al042007.public.022.shtml}}</ref>，[[海地|海地]]从[[太子港|太子港]]一直到多明尼加共和国边界之间地区<ref name="td4public20">{{cite web | author = Richard Knabb | date = 2007-08-17 | title = Hurricane Dean Public Advisory Twenty | publisher = National Hurricane Center | accessdate = 2014-03-12 | url = http://www.nhc.noaa.gov/archive/2007/al04/al042007.public.020.shtml? | archivedate = 2014-01-02 | deadurl = no | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20140102193530/http://www.nhc.noaa.gov/archive/2007/al04/al042007.public.020.shtml}}</ref>，以及[[多明尼加共和国|多明尼加共和国]]从[[巴拉奥纳省|巴拉奥纳省]]到海地边界之间地区都收到飓风警告<ref name="td4public19a">{{cite web | author = Richard Knabb | date = 2007-08-17 | title = Hurricane Dean Intermediate Advisory Nineteen A | publisher = National Hurricane Center | accessdate = 2014-03-12 | archivedate = 2014-01-02 | deadurl = no | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20140102220433/http://www.nhc.noaa.gov/archive/2007/al04/al042007.public_a.019.shtml | url = http://www.nhc.noaa.gov/archive/2007/al04/al042007.public_a.019.shtml?}}</ref>。[[伊斯帕尼奥拉岛|伊斯帕尼奥拉岛]]其他地区<ref name="td4public17">{{cite web | author = Lixion Avila, Michelle Mainelli | date = 2007-08-17 | title = Hurricane Dean Public Advisory Seventeen | publisher = National Hurricane Center | accessdate = 2014-03-12 | archivedate = 2014-01-02 | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20140102220615/http://www.nhc.noaa.gov/archive/2007/al04/al042007.public.017.shtml | url = http://www.nhc.noaa.gov/archive/2007/al04/al042007.public.017.shtml? | deadurl = no}}</ref>以及[[古巴|古巴]]从[[卡马圭省|卡马圭省]]到[[关塔那摩省|关塔那摩省]]之间地区都收到热带风暴警告<ref name="td4public22a">{{cite web | author = Lixion Avila | date = 2007-08-18 | title = Hurricane Dean Intermediate Advisory Twenty Two A | publisher = National Hurricane Center | accessdate = 2014-03-12 | url = http://www.nhc.noaa.gov/archive/2007/al04/al042007.public_a.022.shtml? | archivedate = 2014-01-02 | deadurl = no | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20140102193312/http://www.nhc.noaa.gov/archive/2007/al04/al042007.public_a.022.shtml}}</ref>。数十万居住在低洼和沿海地区的居民撤离<ref name="AFP_2007-08-19_jam">{{cite web | author = Staff Writer | date = 2007-08-19 | title = Monster hurricane bears down on Jamaica | publisher = Agence France-Presse | accessdate = 2014-03-12 | url = http://news.brisbanetimes.com.au/world/monster-hurricane-bears-down-on-jamaica-20070818-u22.html | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20140102193013/http://news.brisbanetimes.com.au/world/monster-hurricane-bears-down-on-jamaica-20070818-u22.html | archivedate = 2014-01-02 | deadurl = no}}</ref>，整个大安的列斯群岛都已启动灾难管理方案<ref name="reliefweb_hispanola_2007-08-18_01">{{cite web | author = World Vision | publisher = Relief Web | date = 2007-08-18 | accessdate = 2014-03-12 | title = As hurricane looms over Caribbean, relief teams prepare: World Vision positioning relief supplies for immediate response when storm hits Hispaniola | archivedate = 2014-03-12 | deadurl = no | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20140312095700/http://reliefweb.int/report/dominican-republic/hurricane-looms-over-caribbean-relief-teams-prepare-world-vision | url = http://reliefweb.int/report/dominican-republic/hurricane-looms-over-caribbean-relief-teams-prepare-world-vision}}</ref><ref name="reliefweb_jam_2007-08-18_02">{{cite web | author = United Nations Office for the Coordination of Humanitarian Affairs (OCHA) | publisher = Relief Web | date = 2007-08-18 | accessdate = 2014-03-12 |title=Hurricane Dean OCHA Situation Report No. 2 | url = http://reliefweb.int/report/barbados/hurricane-dean-ocha-situation-report-no-2 | archivedate = 2014-03-12 | deadurl = no | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20140312095809/http://reliefweb.int/report/barbados/hurricane-dean-ocha-situation-report-no-2}}</ref><ref name="reliefweb_jam_2007-08-18_01">{{cite web | author = Caribbean Disaster Emergency Response Agency (CDERA) | publisher = Relief Web | date = 2007-08-18 | accessdate = 2007-08-26 | title = Hurricane Dean Situation Report #3 | url = http://reliefweb.int/report/barbados/hurricane-dean-situation-report-3 | archivedate = 2014-03-12 | deadurl = no | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20140312095920/http://reliefweb.int/report/barbados/hurricane-dean-situation-report-3}}</ref>。

预计将首当其冲的牙买加做了极其广泛的准备工作。牙买加政府执行长期性的疏散方案，其中包括将该国的[[独立公园|国家体育场]]改建成避难所，把两间[[监狱|最高设防监狱]]的囚犯转移到该处<ref name="SF Gate preps" />。岛上政党暂停为8月27日全国大选进行的竞选活动，以便居民做好应对风暴的准备<ref name="Globe-Mail preps">{{cite news | title = Hurricane Dean bears down on Jamaica | author = Carlos Barria | publisher = Reuters | archivedate = 2014-01-02 | url = http://news.bbc.co.uk/2/hi/americas/6953530.stm | date = 2007-08-19 | accessdate = 2014-03-12 | deadurl = no | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20140102193721/http://news.bbc.co.uk/2/hi/americas/6953530.stm}}</ref>。岛上部分地区实行[[宵禁|宵禁]]，并召回关键岗位的离岗工作人员回到岗位继续工作。超过1000所[[学校|学校]]和[[教堂|教堂]]改建成应急避难所，但风暴来临前只有47个有居民前来躲避。显然，该国的高犯罪率导致岛民担心背离家园后自己的财物会遭到洗劫<ref name="Guardian_2007-08-19_prep">{{cite web | title = Hurricane Dean Pummels Jamaica | author = Howard Campbell | publisher = Washington Post | accessdate = 2014-03-12 | url = http://www.washingtonpost.com/wp-dyn/content/article/2007/08/19/AR2007081901365.html | date = 2007-08-20}}</ref><ref name="BBC_2007-08-19_jam">{{cite web | author = Staff Writer | date = 2007-08-20 | title = Hurricane batters Jamaica's south | publisher = BBC News | accessdate = 2014-03-12 | url = http://news.bbc.co.uk/2/hi/americas/6954296.stm | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20140110113254/http://news.bbc.co.uk/2/hi/americas/6954296.stm | deadurl = no | archivedate = 2014-01-10}}</ref>。[[联合国儿童基金会|联合国儿童基金会]]准备了4个急救包和1000件储水容器，巴拿马航空公司也同意在可能的情况下安排航班将物资在8月22日运往牙买加。[[世界粮食计划署|世界粮食计划署]]在附近的海地准备了存粮，计划在有需要的情况下将之运往牙买加<ref name="reliefweb_jam_2007-08-18_02" />。[[联合国人道主义事务协调厅|联合国灾害评估和协调小组]]试图前往牙买加，但只有一人成功到达，其他人乘坐的航班全部都予以取消<ref name="reliefweb_jam_2007-08-18_02" />。美国方面确认称只要有需要，该国愿意提供援助<ref name="BBC August 19" />，西北加勒比捐助小组召开会议，决定需要采取哪些行动<ref name="reliefweb_jam_2007-08-18_01" />。
[[File:HMS_Portland_F79_DNSD0502434.jpg|thumb]]
气象部门预测伊斯帕尼奥拉岛也将受到这场风暴的严重影响。[[世界展望会|世界展望会]]的工作人员向多明尼加共和国的南方各省提供食品、净水、药品和应急[[发电机|发电机]]，还向收到飓风警告的海地南方省份提供上述物品<ref name="reliefweb_hispanola_2007-08-18_01" />。多明尼加共和国的1580位以及海地的上千位生活在低洼地区的居民随着风暴的逼近而撤离<ref name="AFP_2007-08-19_jam" />。政府官员建议小型船只停在港口内躲避，海地的[[杜桑·卢维杜尔国际机场|杜桑·卢维杜尔国际机场]]暂时关闭<ref name="SF Gate preps" />。

气象部门预测飓风迪安将在[[开曼群岛|开曼群岛]]近海经过，所以预计该[[群岛|群岛]]将会受到惨重打击，[[小开曼|小开曼]]的低洼地区因此强制疏散<ref>{{cite news|url=http://www.caycompass.com/cgi-bin/CFPnews.cgi?ID=1024423 |title=Little Cayman evacuated |publisher=Caymanian Compass |accessdate=2014-03-12 |date=2007-08-18 |author=Staff Writer |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20120206092255/http://www.caycompass.com/cgi-bin/CFPnews.cgi?ID=1024423 |archivedate=2012-02-06 |deadurl=yes }}</ref><ref name=reliefweb_cayman_2007-08-18_02>{{cite web | author = Government of Cayman Islands | publisher = Relief Web | date = 2007-08-18 | accessdate = 2007-08-25 | title = Cayman Islands: Mandatory evacuation | url = http://reliefweb.int/report/cayman-islands/cayman-islands-mandatory-evacuation | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20140312132447/http://reliefweb.int/report/cayman-islands/cayman-islands-mandatory-evacuation | archivedate = 2014-03-12 | deadurl = no}}</ref>，同时也禁止游客上岛<ref name="Newswireca">{{cite news | url = http://www.newswire.ca/en/story/17251/cayman-islands-update-hurricane-dean | title = Cayman Islands Update — Hurricane Dean | accessdate = 2014-03-12 | date = 2007-08-18 | publisher = Cayman Islands Department of Tourism | author = Laura Johnston | archivedate = 2012-07-28 | deadurl = no | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20120728130535/http://www.newswire.ca/en/story/17251/cayman-islands-update-hurricane-dean}}</ref>，还增开多架航班把已经来到岛上的游客撤离<ref name="BBC August 19" /><ref name="Newswireca" />。[[大开曼|大开曼]]和[[开曼布拉克|开曼布拉克]]的学校和市民中心改建成避难所，虽然已经强制撤离，但小开曼还是开设一处避难所以便仍然留在岛上的居民躲避<ref name="reliefweb_cayman_2007-08-18_01">{{cite web | author = Government of Cayman Islands | publisher = Relief Web | date = 2007-08-18 | accessdate = 2014-03-12 | title = Cayman Islands: Shelters open tomorrow | url = http://reliefweb.int/report/cayman-islands/cayman-islands-shelters-open-tomorrow | archivedate = 2014-03-12 | deadurl = no | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20140312133015/http://reliefweb.int/report/cayman-islands/cayman-islands-shelters-open-tomorrow}}</ref>。由于预计飓风将产生灾难性后果，[[英国皇家海军|英国皇家海军]]的“波特兰号”（{{lang|en|HMS ''Portland''}}）[[巡防舰|巡防舰]]和“御浪号”（{{lang|en|RFA ''Wave Ruler''}}）[[补给舰|补给舰]]跟在风暴后方仅240公里外，以求在其吹袭开曼群岛后尽可能快地赶赴当地提供援助<ref name="reliefweb_cayman_2007-08-20_01">{{cite web | author = Government of the United Kingdom | publisher = Relief Web | date = 2007-08-20 | accessdate = 2007-08-25 | title = Cayman Islands: UK Naval ships prepare to assist with hurricane relief effort | archivedate = 2014-03-12 | deadurl = no | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20140312134001/http://reliefweb.int/report/cayman-islands/cayman-islands-uk-naval-ships-prepare-assist-hurricane-relief-effort | url = http://reliefweb.int/report/cayman-islands/cayman-islands-uk-naval-ships-prepare-assist-hurricane-relief-effort}}</ref>。

古巴和波多黎各预计受这场风暴的影响会小得多，因此所做的准备工作也较少。古巴民防部门撤离沿海省份的35万居民<ref name="AFP_2007-08-19_jam" /><ref name="reliefweb_OCHA_2007-08-20">{{cite web | author = United Nations Office for the Coordination of Humanitarian Affairs (OCHA) | date = 2007-08-20 | title = Hurricane Dean OCHA Situation Report No. 4 | publisher = Relief Web | accessdate = 2014-03-12 | archivedate = 2014-03-12 | deadurl = no | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20140312134656/http://reliefweb.int/report/jamaica/hurricane-dean-ocha-situation-report-no-4 | url = http://reliefweb.int/report/jamaica/hurricane-dean-ocha-situation-report-no-4}}</ref>。[[哈瓦那|哈瓦那]]政府在风暴来临前中止所有[[旅游|旅游]]项目<ref name="BBC August 19" />。军人和应急官员准备将学校和其他政府大楼改建为临时避难所，但之后风暴的行进路径表明没有必要这么做<ref name="SF Gate preps" />。美国[[联邦紧急事务管理局|联邦紧急事务管理局]]派出一支由五位成员组成的小队在飓风来袭前到达波多黎各，他们配备卫星通讯系统，可以提供可视电话会议并协助对风暴造成的任何破坏做出实时性的评估<ref name="ENS_dean_prep_01">{{cite web|author=Staff Writer |date=2007-08-17 |title=Gulf States Mop Up After Erin, Ramp Up for Hurricane Dean |publisher=Environmental News Service |accessdate=2014-10-28 |url=http://www.ens-newswire.com/ens/aug2007/2007-08-17-02.asp |deadurl=yes |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20141028221750/http://www.ens-newswire.com/ens/aug2007/2007-08-17-02.asp |archivedate=2014-10-28 }}</ref>。

=== 墨西哥 ===
[[File:Dean_21_aug_2007_1905Z.jpg|thumb]]
由于对飓风迪安的行进路径预测准确，并且预告的提前时间也比较长<ref name="Dean_5_day_cone">{{cite web | author = NHC | publisher = National Oceanic and Atmospheric Administration | date = 2007-08-22 | accessdate = 2014-03-12 | title = 5-Day Track Forecast Cone and Watch/Warning | archivedate = 2014-01-02 | deadurl = no | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20140102193555/http://www.nhc.noaa.gov/archive/2007/graphics/al04/loop_5W.shtml | url = http://www.nhc.noaa.gov/archive/2007/graphics/al04/loop_5W.shtml}}</ref>，因此[[墨西哥政府|墨西哥政府]]可以做出充分的准备。8月17日，预计风暴将会登陆的金塔纳罗奥州宣布进入[[紧急状态|紧急状态]]，并于次日开始疏散游客<ref name="France24_07-08-18">{{cite web | author = AFP | date = 2007-08-21 | title = Hurricane Dean turns deadly | publisher = France 24 | accessdate = 2007-08-19 | deadurl = yes | archivedate = 2007-09-30 | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20070930185626/http://www.france24.com/france24Public/en/news/world/20070819-dean-hurricane-jamaica-yucatan-catergory-four.html | url = http://www.france24.com/france24Public/en/news/world/20070819-dean-hurricane-jamaica-yucatan-catergory-four.html}}</ref>和该州那些生活在最容易受到影响地区的居民<ref name="Globe-Mail preps" /><ref name="esmas state of emergency">{{cite web|title=Declara SEGOB emergencia en Quintana Roo |archivedate=2013-04-11 |deadurl=yes |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20130411085938/http://www.esmas.com/noticierostelevisa/mexico/654298.html |url=http://www.esmas.com/noticierostelevisa/mexico/654298.html |author=Staff writer |publisher=Notimex |date=2007-08-17 |accessdate=2014-03-12 }}</ref>。该州政府将学校和其他公共建筑设立为避难所<ref name="reliefweb_2007-08-19_02" />，并准备应急物资。金塔纳罗奥州西北部相邻的[[尤卡坦州|尤卡坦州]]宣布进入绿色警戒状态<ref name="Yucatán green alert">{{cite web|title=Preparativos en Yucatán por el huracán Dean |deadurl=yes |url=http://www.yucatan.com.mx/noticia.asp?cx=11$3403000000$3620633&f=20070817 |date=2007-08-17 |accessdate=2007-08-18 |author=Staff writer |publisher=Diario de Yucatán |archivedate=2007-11-12 |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20071112013557/http://www.yucatan.com.mx/noticia.asp?cx=11%243403000000%243620633&f=20070817 }}</ref>。8月19日，尤卡坦半岛从[[切图马尔|切图马尔]]到[[圣费利佩_(墨西哥)|圣费利佩]]（{{lang|en|San Felipe}}）之间地区收到飓风观察预警，居民也开始进行最后时刻的准备工作<ref name="td4public26">{{cite web | author = James Franklin, Jamie Rhome | date = 2007-08-19 | title = Hurricane Dean Public Advisory Twenty Six | publisher = National Hurricane Center | accessdate = 2014-03-12 | url = http://www.nhc.noaa.gov/archive/2007/al04/al042007.public.026.shtml? | archivedate = 2014-01-02 | deadurl = no | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20140102193443/http://www.nhc.noaa.gov/archive/2007/al04/al042007.public.026.shtml}}</ref>。

=== 伯利兹 ===
[[伯利兹市|伯利兹市]]以北的沿海地区收到飓风警告，预计风速将高达每小时240公里<ref name="BBC_2007-08-21_Mex03">{{cite web | author = BBC Staff Writer | date = 2007-08-21 | title = Hurricane Dean hits Mexico coast | publisher = BBC | accessdate = 2014-03-12 | url = http://news.bbc.co.uk/2/hi/americas/6955163.stm | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20121203125906/http://news.bbc.co.uk/2/hi/americas/6955163.stm | archivedate = 2012-12-03 | deadurl = no}}</ref>。政府在伯利兹市到墨西哥边境之间区域从[[黄昏|黄昏]]到[[黎明|黎明]]时段实行宵禁<ref name="NPR_Belize_21-08-2007" />。8月17日，[[伯利兹总理|伯利兹总理]][[赛义德·穆萨|赛义德·穆萨]]（{{lang|en|Said Musa}}）主持两轮伯利兹全国应急管理机构的会议<ref name="reliefweb_2007-08-19_02" />，他指示新创立的海岸警卫队使用船只和飞机撤离热门旅游景点[[安伯格里斯岛|安伯格里斯岛]]和[[库尔刻岛|库尔刻岛]]（{{lang|en|Caye Caulker}}）的游客<ref name="NPR_Belize_21-08-2007">{{cite web | author = NPR.org | publisher = National Public Radio | date = 2007-08-21 | accessdate = 2014-03-12 | title = Hurricane Dean Weakens, Expected to Spare Texas | archivedate = 2014-03-08 | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20140308064224/http://www.npr.org/templates/story/story.php?storyId=13817871 | deadurl = no | url = http://www.npr.org/templates/story/story.php?storyId=13817871}}</ref><ref name="SanPedro_Belize_01">{{cite web|author=James Janmohamed |date=2007-08-18 |title=San Pedro prepares for evacuation |publisher=San Pedro Daily |accessdate=2014-03-12 |url=http://www.sanpedrodaily.com/8-18-07.html |archivedate=2012-07-18 |deadurl=yes |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20120718064136/http://www.sanpedrodaily.com/8-18-07.html }}</ref>。政府还疏散伯利兹市的三所[[医院|医院]]，将高危患者转移到内陆的[[首都|首都]][[贝尔墨邦|贝尔墨邦]]。市长也敦促居民尽快离开伯利兹市，前往首都的避难所中躲避<ref name="NPR_Belize_21-08-2007" />。

联合国灾害评估和协调小组派遣两位成员前往伯利兹市，其他人则到达贝尔墨邦<ref name="reliefweb_OCHA_2007-08-20" />。[[橘园区|橘园区]]和[[科罗萨尔区|科罗萨尔区]]储存有政府物资供风暴过后的救灾使用<ref name="reliefweb_OCHA_2007-08-20" /><ref name="reliefweb_2007-08-19_02" />。[[国际红十字与红新月运动|红十字会]]和[[泛美卫生组织|泛美卫生组织]]的关键设备储存在联合国儿童基金会位于伯利兹市的大楼内，该市的联合国大楼也改建成危机处理中心<ref name="reliefweb_OCHA_2007-08-20" />。

=== 墨西哥湾 ===
[[File:Gulf_Offshore_Platform.jpg|thumb]]都因预计飓风迪安来袭而疏散。]]
市场分析认为飓风迪安如果像预期的那样进入加勒比海，那么会对炼油能力产生影响，这导致8月15日的[[石油|石油]][[期货|期货]]出现飙升<ref name="MarketWatch_01">{{cite web | author = Polya Lesova | date = 2007-08-15 | title = Crude oil, natural gas rise sharply on storm worries | publisher = MarketWatch | accessdate = 2007-08-15 | archivedate = 2014-01-03 | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20140103082052/http://www.marketwatch.com/story/oil-ends-higher-on-storm-worries-supply-drop | deadurl = no | url = http://www.marketwatch.com/story/oil-ends-higher-on-storm-worries-supply-drop}}</ref><ref name="detroitfp_oil_01">{{cite web | author = Alejandro Bodipo-Memba | date = 2007-08-16 | title = When gas prices go up, blame Dean | publisher = Detroit Free Press | accessdate = 2014-03-12 | archivedate = 2014-01-02 | deadurl = no | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20140102212502/http://www.nhc.noaa.gov/archive/2007/al04/al042007.fstadv.011.shtml | url = http://www.nhc.noaa.gov/archive/2007/al04/al042007.fstadv.011.shtml?}}</ref>。[[瑞士越洋钻探公司|瑞士越洋钻探公司]]于8月15日晚从[[新奥尔良|新奥尔良]]东南方向260公里外海域的一个[[石油平台|石油钻井平台]]上撤离11位非必需职工，但还有约125名人员留在平台上<ref name="Oil rig evacuations">{{cite news | title = Storm-Drenched Texas Prepare for Hurricane Dean | agency = Associated Press | author = Staff writer | date = 2007-08-16 | accessdate = 2007-08-17}}</ref>。次日[[荷兰皇家壳牌|荷兰皇家壳牌]]疏散275名辅助人员，然后又因[[2007年热带风暴埃林|热带风暴埃林]]撤离188人<ref name="Forbes_impact&preps">{{cite news | author = Guy Ellis | agency = Associated Press | title = Hurricane Dean Gains Power in Caribbean | date = 2007-08-17 | accessdate = 2014-03-12 | url = http://www.washingtonpost.com/wp-dyn/content/article/2007/08/17/AR2007081700298.html}}</ref>。

2007年8月18日，墨西哥湾多口油井关闭，其总产量可以达到每天1640[[立方米|立方米]]原油和31方立方米[[天然气|天然气]]，占整个海湾原油产量的0.8%。到{{lang|en|UTC}}当天下午16点30分，已经有两口钻井和一个[[石油平台|平台]]上的人员撤离<ref name="Oil shutins 08-18">{{cite web | author = Minerals Management Service | publisher = United States Department of Interior | date = 2007-08-18 | accessdate = 2007-08-18 | title = Hurricane Dean Statistics Update | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20100706171259/http://www.mms.gov/ooc/press/2007/press0818.htm | archivedate = 2010-07-06 | deadurl = yes | url = http://www.mms.gov/ooc/press/2007/press0818.htm}}</ref>。

墨西哥国有的[[墨西哥石油公司|墨西哥石油公司]]于8月19日迪安来袭前做好停止原油开采的准备<ref name="BBC August 19">{{cite news | title = Jamaica alert as Dean threatens | agency = BBC News | date = 2007-08-19 | author = Staff writer}}</ref>，动用55艘船只和29架[[直升机|直升机]]从超过140个石油平台上撤离13360位职工<ref name="AFP_2007-08-19_jam" />。随着风暴继续强化，墨西哥石油公司撤离的员工数量在8月20日增加到18000人，全部407口油井或钻井作业均予中止。这令世界原油和天然气产量每天分别减少42.1万立方米和7400万立方米<ref name="Miami_Herald_jam_01">{{cite news | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20100713095125/http://www.jameslogancourier.org/index.php?itemid=2395 | author = David Ovalle, Jacqueline Charles and Martin Merzer | date = 2007-08-20 | title = Dean's rain reaches Mexico; damage reported in Jamaica | publisher = Miami Herald | url = http://www.jameslogancourier.org/index.php?itemid=2395 | accessdate = 2014-03-08 | archivedate = 2010-07-13 | deadurl = yes }}</ref>。

=== 其他地区 ===
整个加勒比海约有十余艘游船改变航向以求避开飓风迪安<ref name="Forbes_impact&preps" />。[[洪都拉斯|洪都拉斯]]进入48小时的警戒状态，特别是该国北部[[洪都拉斯行政区划|省份]]。[[海湾群岛省|海湾群岛省]]进入红色警戒状态，还准备多处应急场所，必要情况下可以容纳一万人<ref>{{cite news | title = Autoridades decretan alerta roja en Islas de la Bahía | url = http://www.laprensahn.com/ediciones/2007/08/20/autoridades_decretan_alerta_roja_en_islas_de_la_bahia | publisher = La Prensa | date = 2007-08-19 | accessdate = 2007-08-20 | deadurl = yes | archivedate = 2008-01-02 | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20080102234850/http://www.laprensahn.com/ediciones/2007/08/20/autoridades_decretan_alerta_roja_en_islas_de_la_bahia |author = Cathy Rose}}</ref>。

美国[[路易斯安那州|路易斯安那州]][[州长|州长]]国土安全和应急准备办公室于8月16日启动危机行动小组，对风暴进行监控并协调准备工作<ref name="ENS_dean_prep_01" />。州长[[凯瑟琳·布兰科|凯瑟琳·布兰科]]于8月17日傍晚宣布全州进入紧急状态<ref name="louisiana_blanco_01">{{cite web | author = Associated Press | date = 2007-08-17 | title = Blanco declares state of emergency | publisher = WWLTV | accessdate = 2007-08-18 | deadurl = yes | url = http://www.wwltv.com/topstories/stories/wwl081707blanco.440718ba.html | archivedate = 2008-01-25 | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20080125231439/http://www.wwltv.com/topstories/stories/wwl081707blanco.440718ba.html}}</ref>，还要求[[美国总统|美国总统]]作出紧急声明，允许该州在风暴登陆前获得联邦基金<ref name="ENS_dean_prep_01" />。[[德克萨斯州|德克萨斯州]]州长[[里克·佩里|里克·佩里]]宣布迪安对该州构成迫在眉睫的威胁，因此早在风暴还至少要五天后才可能来袭的8月17日开始全面的飓风防备工作<ref name="texas_perry_01">{{cite web | author = Governor Rick Perry | year = 2007 | title = Gov. Perry Declares Hurricane Dean Imminent Threat to Texas | publisher = Office of the Governor | accessdate = 2014-03-12 | archivedate = 2013-06-15 | deadurl = yes | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20130615052409/http://governor.state.tx.us/news/press-release/2173/ | url = http://governor.state.tx.us/news/press-release/2173/ }}</ref>。德克萨斯州曾于6月到7日因热带降雨带北上产生的大量降雨导致严重的洪涝灾害，热带风暴埃林也令地面含水仍处于饱和状态。州长佩里担心迪安会带来更多的降水，导致再度出现山洪爆发<ref name="forbes_texas_flooding">
{{cite news | author = Elizabeth White | year = 2007 | title = Texas Soaked by Erin, Braces for Dean | publisher = Forbes | url = http://www.highbeam.com/doc/1Y1-109521598.html | via = HighBeam Research | accessdate = 2014-03-12 | archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20140611091108/http://www.highbeam.com/doc/1Y1-109521598.html | archive-date = 2014-06-11 | dead-url = yes }}
</ref>，还安排250位[[德克萨斯州公园和野生动物部|德克萨斯州公园和野生动物部]]工作人员准备好船只待命，准备对可能需要的疏散工作提供协助。他派遣大量[[德州军队|德州军队]]官兵建立应急避难所，并且有意派出上万人加入<ref name="ENS_dean_prep_01" />。德克萨斯州的燃料产业开始增加沿海各[[县_(美国)|县]]的燃料储备，确保在飓风来袭下仍然会有足够的燃油分配<ref name="ENS_dean_prep_01" />。[[德克萨斯州交通部|德克萨斯州交通部]]开始针对可能需要的撤离工作准备更多疏散车道和可变车道<ref name="ENS_dean_prep_01" />。[[美国国家航空航天局|美国国家航空航天局]]缩短[[STS-118|STS-118]]的任务时间，以防迪安逼近位于[[休斯敦|休斯敦]][[林顿·约翰逊太空中心|林顿·约翰逊太空中心]]的[[小克里斯托弗·C·卡夫任务控制中心|任务控制中心]]<ref name="Herald preps">{{cite news | url = http://www.ledger-enquirer.com/2007/08/18/111329_storm-warnings-posted-in-jamaica.html | title = Storm warnings posted in Jamaica, Caymans | author = Jacqueline Charles | coauthors = Jim Wyss and Martin Merzer | publisher = The Miami Herald | date = 2007-08-18 | accessdate = 2014-03-13 | deadurl = yes | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20140313013425/http://www.ledger-enquirer.com/2007/08/18/111329_storm-warnings-posted-in-jamaica.html | archivedate = 2014-03-13 }}</ref>，为此，任务管理者将最后一次[[太空行走|太空行走]]的时间缩短了两个[[小时|小时]]<ref name="WSJ NASA">{{cite news | author = Staff writer | publisher = Associated Press | title = Hurricane Dean Forces NASA To Scale Back Final Spacewalk | date = 2007-08-18 }}</ref>，让机组可以比原计划提前一天返回[[地球|地球]]<ref name="SF Gate preps" /><ref name="NASA status report 20">{{cite web | archivedate = 2013-08-12 | deadurl = no | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20130812230605/http://www.nasa.gov/mission_pages/shuttle/shuttlemissions/sts118/news/STS-118-20.html | url = http://www.nasa.gov/mission_pages/shuttle/shuttlemissions/sts118/news/STS-118-20.html | author = Mission Control Center | publisher = National Aeronautics and Space Administration | accessdate = 2014-03-13 | date = 2007-08-18 | title = STS-118 MCC Status Report #20}}</ref>。

