一共有15个不同国家受到飓风迪安的影响，加勒比海区域有42人死亡。风暴首先于2007年8月17日冲击小安的列斯群岛，然后其外围在通过加勒比海期间又横扫大安的列斯群岛。风暴以四级飓风强度经过牙买加，再增强为五级飓风并于8月21日登陆墨西哥尤卡坦半岛。8月22日的第二次登陆产生的影响较小。

=== 小安的列斯群岛 ===
迪安于8月17日以二级飓风强度穿过圣卢西亚海峡进入[[加勒比地区|加勒比地区]]<ref name="td4disc17" />，并快速从小安的列斯群岛的圣卢西亚和马提尼克岛之间经过<ref name="td4disc17" />，其雨带和产生的[[风暴潮|风暴潮]]对沿途的每一个岛屿都构成影响<ref name="TCR" />。马提尼克受到的破坏最为严重，总计经济损失估计达到4亿[[欧元|欧元]]，还间接导致三人死亡，附近的瓜德罗普岛也遭受4亿欧元的破坏。圣卢西亚受到的损失约有1.8亿美元，其中大部分是因巨浪导致<ref name="TCR" />。

马提尼克遭遇的持续风速有每小时120公里，阵风时速达到170公里<ref name="td4disc17" />。风暴产生高达332毫米的倾盆大雨<ref name="TCR" />导致岛上岛上到处都出现洪水，[[市镇_(法国)|市镇]]里维耶尔皮洛特（{{lang|fr|Rivière-Pilote}}）完全被洪水淹没。马提尼克大部分居民家中停电、停水，缺少食物，电话线路也被中断，还有600位岛民无家可归<ref name="cab360_2007-08-21">{{cite web | author = Staff Writer | date = 2007-08-20 | title = Heavy losses for Martinique; Eastern Caribbean reopens after Dean | publisher = Caribbean360 | accessdate = 2007-08-22 | url = http://www.caribbean360.com/index.php/weather/12301.html#axzz2vnxg1EWl | archivedate = 2014-01-02}}</ref><ref name = "Sydney impact">{{cite web | archivedate = 2013-10-23 | deadurl = no | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20121023030351/http://www.smh.com.au/news/world/hurricane-dean-intensifies/2007/08/18/1186857814654.html | url = http://www.smh.com.au/news/world/hurricane-dean-intensifies/2007/08/18/1186857814654.html | title = Hurricane Dean intensifies | publisher = Agence France-Presse | author = Staff writer | date = 2007-08-18 | accessdate = 2014-03-13}}</ref><ref name="carib_news_2007-08-23">{{cite web | author = Danik Ibraheem Zandwonis | publisher = Caribbean Net News | date = 2007-08-23 | accessdate = 2014-03-13 | title = Guadeloupe and Martinique after Dean | url = http://www.caribbeannewsnow.com/caribnet/martinique/martinique.php?news_id=3166&start=40&category_id=34 | archive-date = 2014-02-25 | archive-url = https://archive.is/20140225190419/http://www.caribbeannewsnow.com/caribnet/martinique/martinique.php?news_id=3166&start=40&category_id=34 | dead-url = no }}</ref>。岛上所有的[[香蕉|香蕉]]作物以及70%的甘蔗种植园都被风暴摧毁<ref>{{cite web|archivedate=2012-10-26 |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20121026051408/http://www.canada.com/topics/news/world/story.html?id=a8b3574c-38b9-4843-8ec3-8c550c33a27b |url=http://www.canada.com/topics/news/world/story.html?id=a8b3574c-38b9-4843-8ec3-8c550c33a27b |title=Hurricane destroys Martinique, Guadeloupe bananas |publisher=Reuters |author=Staff writer |date=2007-08-18 |accessdate=2014-03-13 |deadurl=yes }}</ref>，该岛遭受的4亿欧元损失中大部分都来源于这两种农作物。

8月16日晚，距风暴到达圣卢西亚还有12小时，该岛部分居民家中已经开始出现停电情况。当晚岛上出现大雨和雷阵雨，[[黑瓦诺拉国际机场|黑瓦诺拉国际机场]]的降雨量有40毫米<ref>{{cite web | author = Computer Generated | publisher = Weather Underground | date = 2007-08-16 | accessdate = 2014-03-13 | title = History for Hewanorra, St. Lucia: Thursday, August 16, 2007 | url = http://www.wunderground.com/history/airport/TLPL/2007/8/16/DailyHistory.html?req_city=NA&req_state=NA&req_statename=NA | archivedate = 2014-01-02 | deadurl = no | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20140102194158/http://www.wunderground.com/history/airport/TLPL/2007/8/16/DailyHistory.html?req_city=NA&req_state=NA&req_statename=NA}}</ref><ref>{{cite web | author = Computer Generated | publisher = Weather Underground | date = 2007-08-17 | accessdate = 2014-03-13 | title = History for Hewanorra, St. Lucia: Friday, August 17, 2007 | archivedate = 2014-01-02 | deadurl = no | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20140102192525/http://www.wunderground.com/history/airport/TLPL/2007/8/17/DailyHistory.html?req_city=NA&req_state=NA&req_statename=NA | url = http://www.wunderground.com/history/airport/TLPL/2007/8/17/DailyHistory.html?req_city=NA&req_state=NA&req_statename=NA}}</ref>。到了早上，岛上的风速已有每小时145公里，达到飓风强度<ref name="cabnews_2007-08-18">{{cite web | author = Amselma Aimable | date = 2007-08-18 | title = Report from St Lucia | publisher = Caribbean Net News | accessdate = 2014-03-13 | url = http://www.caribbeannewsnow.com/caribnet/archivelist.php?pageaction=showdetail&news_id=3095&arcyear=2007&arcmonth=8&arcday=18 | archive-date = 2014-03-12 | archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20140312212342/http://www.caribbeannewsnow.com/caribnet/archivelist.php?pageaction=showdetail&news_id=3095&arcyear=2007&arcmonth=8&arcday=18 | dead-url = no }}</ref>，许多树木被连根拔起<ref name="BBC News August 17" />，还刮倒多条电线杆，桥梁因此封闭，还引发[[山崩|山崩]]并破坏多户房屋的屋顶。圣卢西亚的首都[[卡斯特里|卡斯特里]]被风暴潮淹没，街头可以看到渔船。岛屿中部小镇萨罗特（{{lang|en|Sarrot}}）河水暴涨，有一人试图救回一头牛时被水卷走而丧生<ref name="Forbes_impact&preps" /><ref name="bbc_2007-08-17_02">{{cite web | author = BBC NEWS | date = 2007-08-17 | title = Caribbean storm gathers strength | publisher = BBC News | accessdate = 2014-03-13 | archivedate = 2014-01-02 | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20140102193327/http://news.bbc.co.uk/2/hi/americas/6950626.stm | deadurl = no | url = http://news.bbc.co.uk/2/hi/americas/6950626.stm}}</ref>。飓风迪安破坏岛上两所医院的屋顶，不过幸运的是没有人员因此受伤<ref name="paho_2007-08-21" /><ref name="ctv_2007-08-17_01">{{cite web | author = CTV.ca News Staff | date = 2007-08-17 | title = Hurricane Dean upgraded to powerful Category 4 | publisher = CTV.ca | accessdate = 2007-08-17 | deadurl = yes | archivedate = 2007-08-23 | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20070823013646/http://www.ctv.ca/servlet/ArticleNews/story/CTVNews/20070817/dean_storm_070817/20070817?hub=CTVNewsAt11 | url = http://www.ctv.ca/servlet/ArticleNews/story/CTVNews/20070817/dean_storm_070817/20070817?hub=CTVNewsAt11}}</ref>。另外还有多幢建筑物受损，其中大部分位于该岛北部沿岸区域，这里受到的飓风吹袭最为猛烈<ref name="reliefweb_2007-08-21_05">{{cite web | author = United Nations Office for the Coordination of Humanitarian Affairs (OCHA) | date = 2007-08-21 | title = Hurricane Dean OCHA Situation Report No. 5 | publisher = Relief Web | accessdate = 2014-03-13 | url = http://reliefweb.int/report/mexico/hurricane-dean-ocha-situation-report-no-5 |archivedate = 2014-03-13 | deadurl = no | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20140313030349/http://reliefweb.int/report/mexico/hurricane-dean-ocha-situation-report-no-5}}</ref>。该国教育部长报告有11所学校共计遭受价值30万[[东加勒比元|东加勒比元]]的破坏<ref name="CDERA_2007-08-21_7">{{cite web | author = CDERA | date = 2007-08-21 | accessdate = 2007-08-22 | publisher = CDERA.org | title = CDERA Mounts Level Two Response to Hurricane Dean Impact Update August 21, 2007, 4 p.m. EDT | url = http://www.cdera.org/cunews/uploads/hurricane_deansitrep7.pdf | format = PDF | archivedate = 2012-09-05 | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20120905133116/http://www.cdera.org/cunews/uploads/hurricane_deansitrep7.pdf | deadurl = yes}}</ref>，全国范围内的住房和建筑物总计受到约80万东加勒比元的损失<ref name="CDERA_2007-08-21_7" />。通讯、工程、交通和公共事业部报告该国的主要[[基础设施|基础设施]]仍然正常，没有出现长期瘫痪的情况<ref name="reliefweb_2007-08-21_05" /><ref name="CDERA_2007-08-21_7" />。

圣卢西亚的农业地區遭受的打击最为沉重，多达20平方公里的香蕉农场受到严重破坏，许多种植园被水淹或是直接摧毁<ref name="cabnews_2007-08-18" /><ref name="cbc_2007-08-17">{{cite web |date=2007-08-17 |title=Hurricane claims one life in St. Lucia and possibly two in Dominica |author=Staff Writer |publisher=CBC |accessdate=2007-08-17 |url=http://www.cbc.bb/content/view/12195/45/ |archiveurl=https://www.webcitation.org/5axkRsHjT?url=http://www.evernetcorp.com/content/view/12195/45/ |deadurl=yes |archivedate=2008-09-20 }}</ref>。全岛平均损失75%的庄稼，北部农场田地中损失的有80%，罗索谷（{{lang|en|Roseau Valley}}）更达到85%。农业受损总额达到1320万东加勒比元，整个圣卢西亚因飓风迪安受到的损失也达到1730万东加勒比元，占该国[[国内生产总值|国内生产总值]]的0.5%<ref name="CDERA_2007-08-21_7" /><ref name="stlucia_gdp">{{cite web | author = CIA | date = 2007-08-16 | publisher = Central Intelligence Agency | accessdate = 2014-03-13 | title = St. Lucia: Economy | url = https://www.cia.gov/library/publications/the-world-factbook/geos/st.html | archive-date = 2016-01-30 | archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20160130185933/https://www.cia.gov/library/publications/the-world-factbook/geos/st.html | dead-url = no }}</ref><ref name="reliefweb_2007-08-22">{{cite web | author = Food and Agriculture Organization of the United Nations (FAO) | date = 2007-08-22 | title = Thousands in need of humanitarian assistance after Hurricane Dean | publisher = Relief Web | accessdate = 2007-08-23 | url = http://reliefweb.int/report/dominica/thousands-need-humanitarian-assistance-after-hurricane-dean | archivedate = 2014-03-13 | deadurl = no | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20140313062820/http://reliefweb.int/report/dominica/thousands-need-humanitarian-assistance-after-hurricane-dean}}</ref>。

=== 大安的列斯群岛 ===
[[File:House_in_Kingston_after_Hurricane_Dean.jpg|thumb]]摧毁的一套房屋]]
风暴从大安的列斯群岛的大部分岛屿南部海域经过，不过其外部雨带穿过许多岛屿，给牙买加带去飓风强度狂风，波多黎各、古巴和开曼群岛大多得以幸免<ref name="milenio_08_18">{{cite web | author = Staff Writer | date = 2007-08-18 | title = Se aleja huracán "Dean" de Puerto Rico sin causar daños | publisher = Milenio | accessdate = 2014-03-13 | url = http://noticiasdelagua.blogspot.com/2007/08/1340-se-aleja-huracn-dean-de-puerto.html | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20140104165204/http://noticiasdelagua.blogspot.com/2007/08/1340-se-aleja-huracn-dean-de-puerto.html | archivedate = 2014-01-04 | deadurl = no}}</ref>，考虑到飓风迪安经过的路线距牙买加南部海岸仅有80到95公里，并且强度达到四级，这样的结果实属幸运<ref name="TCR" /><ref name="td4public27">{{cite web | author = James Franklin, Jamie Rhome | date = 2007-08-19 | title = Hurricane Dean Public Advisory Twenty Seven | publisher = National Hurricane Center | accessdate = 2014-03-13 | archivedate = 2014-01-02 | deadurl = no | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20140102223812/http://www.nhc.noaa.gov/archive/2007/al04/al042007.public.027.shtml | url = http://www.nhc.noaa.gov/archive/2007/al04/al042007.public.027.shtml?}}</ref>。牙买加东部因大雨导致山洪爆发，最东北部还出现了山体滑坡<ref name="BBC_2007-08-19_jam" />。经确认至少有两人直接因风暴遇难<ref name="reliefweb_jam_OPDEM_2007-08-20">{{cite web | author = Government of Jamaica | date = 2007-08-20 | title = Jamaica OPDEM Situation Report No. 8 | publisher = Relief Web | accessdate = 2014-03-13 | archivedate = 2014-03-13 | url = http://reliefweb.int/report/jamaica/jamaica-opdem-situation-report-no-8 | deadurl = no | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20140313064942/http://reliefweb.int/report/jamaica/jamaica-opdem-situation-report-no-8}}</ref>。超过1500套房屋的屋顶被毁，其中大部分是由飓风强度的狂风造成<ref name="reliefweb_jam_USAID_2007-08-24">{{cite web | author = Government of Jamaica | publisher = Relief Web | date = 2007-08-24 | accessdate = 2007-08-26 | title = Jamaica: USAID hands over emergency relief supplies | archivedate = 2014-03-13 | url = http://reliefweb.int/report/jamaica/jamaica-usaid-hands-over-emergency-relief-supplies | deadurl = no | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20140313065143/http://reliefweb.int/report/jamaica/jamaica-usaid-hands-over-emergency-relief-supplies}}</ref>，还有3127套民宅受损，其中1582户已无法居住<ref name="reliefweb_factsheet_2007-08-24">{{cite web | author = United States Agency for International Development (USAID) | publisher = Relief Web | date = 2007-08-24 | accessdate = 2007-08-26 | title = Latin America and the Caribbean – Hurricane Season 2007 Fact Sheet #3 (FY 2007) | url = http://reliefweb.int/report/belize/latin-america-and-caribbean-hurricane-season-2007-fact-sheet-3-fy-2007 | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20140313065355/http://reliefweb.int/report/belize/latin-america-and-caribbean-hurricane-season-2007-fact-sheet-3-fy-2007 | archivedate = 2014-03-13 | deadurl = no}}</ref>。山崩和倒塌的树木封死了数百条道路，尤其以东北部的乡村地区情况严重<ref name="reliefweb_jam_OPDEM_2007-08-21">{{cite web | author = Government of Jamaica | publisher = Relief Web | date = 2007-08-21 | accessdate = 2007-08-26 | title = Jamaica OPDEM Situation Report No. 9 | url = http://reliefweb.int/report/jamaica/jamaica-opdem-situation-report-no-9 | archivedate = 2014-03-13 | deadurl = no | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20140313065558/http://reliefweb.int/report/jamaica/jamaica-opdem-situation-report-no-9}}</ref><ref name="reliefweb_jam_cleanup_2007-08-22">{{cite web | author = Government of Jamaica | date = 2007-08-22 | title = Jamaica: Post-Hurricane Dean clean-up activities continues | publisher = Relief Web | accessdate = 2007-08-26 | url = http://reliefweb.int/report/jamaica/jamaica-post-hurricane-dean-clean-activities-continues | archivedate = 2014-03-13 | deadurl = no | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20140313065704/http://reliefweb.int/report/jamaica/jamaica-post-hurricane-dean-clean-activities-continues}}</ref>。与小安的列斯群岛类似，牙买加也遭受了沉重的农业损失。共计失去了40%的[[甘蔗|甘蔗]]作物，80%到100%的香蕉作物，75%已经成长到第三年的[[咖啡属|咖啡树]]，还有最外层可可作物的20%<ref name="reliefweb_factsheet_2007-08-24" />。飓风迪安影响到了248条道路，其中有186条堵塞<ref name="reliefweb_jam_OPDEM_2007-08-21" /><ref name="reliefweb_jam_cleanup_2007-08-22" />，有十条位于[[京斯敦|京斯敦]][[都会区|都会区]]<ref name="reliefweb_jam_OPDEM_2007-08-21" />，[[圣安德鲁区_(牙买加)|圣安德鲁区]]也有14条路段封死，[[圣凯瑟琳区|圣凯瑟琳区]]有43条道路封堵，西部地区（[[圣詹姆斯区_(牙买加)|圣詹姆斯区]]、[[汉诺威区|汉诺威区]]、[[威斯特摩兰区_(牙买加)|威斯特摩兰区]]和[[特里洛尼区|特里洛尼区]]）情况较好，一共只有8条路被封，而东北区域则有多达100条道路堵死<ref name="reliefweb_jam_cleanup_2007-08-22" />。
[[File:Hurricane_Dean_Bull_Bay_damage.jpg|left]]公牛湾受到严重破坏]]
迪安在伊斯帕尼奥拉岛以南约270公里外经过，该岛上的海地和多明尼加共和国因此避开了风暴的大部分风力<ref name="td4public23">{{cite web | author = Lixion Avila | title = Hurricane Dean Public Advisory Twenty Three | publisher = National Hurricane Center | accessdate = 2014-03-13 | date = 2007-08-18 | archivedate = 2014-01-02 | deadurl = no | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20140102193533/http://www.nhc.noaa.gov/archive/2007/al04/al042007.public.023.shtml | url = http://www.nhc.noaa.gov/archive/2007/al04/al042007.public.023.shtml?}}</ref><ref name="Dom_today_08-19-07">{{cite web | author = Staff Writer | date = 2007-08-18 | title = Dominican Republic feels effects of Hurricane Dean | publisher = Dominican Republic News | accessdate = 2014-03-13 | archivedate = 2014-01-02 | deadurl = yes | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20140102194515/http://www.dominicantoday.com/dr/local/2007/8/18/25136/Dominican-Republic-feels-effects-of-Hurricane-Dean | url = http://www.dominicantoday.com/dr/local/2007/8/18/25136/Dominican-Republic-feels-effects-of-Hurricane-Dean }}</ref>。尽管如此，两国还是有15人丧生<ref name="AFP_2007-08-19_jam" /><ref name="reliefweb_2007-08-19_02">{{cite web | author = United Nations Office for the Coordination of Humanitarian Affairs (OCHA) | publisher = Relief Web | date = 2007-08-19 | accessdate = 2014-03-13 | title = Hurricane Dean OCHA Situation Report No. 3 | archivedate = 2013-02-24 | url = http://reliefweb.int/report/belize/hurricane-dean-ocha-situation-report-no-3 | deadurl = no | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20130224233917/http://reliefweb.int/report/belize/hurricane-dean-ocha-situation-report-no-3}}</ref><ref name="OCHA_2007-08-24_01">{{cite report | author = United Nations Office for the Coordination of Humanitarian Affairs | publisher = United Nations Office for the Coordination of Humanitarian Affairs | date = 2007-08-24 | accessdate = 2007-08-26 | title = Situation Report 7 – Hurricane Dean — August 24, 2007}}</ref>。暴雨淹没了[[圣多明哥|圣多明哥]]的多条街道<ref name="reliefweb_2007-08-21">{{cite web | author = United Nations Office for the Coordination of Humanitarian Affairs (OCHA) | publisher = Relief Web | date = 2007-08-21 | accessdate = 2014-03-13 | title = Hurricane Dean OCHA Situation Report No. 5 | url = http://reliefweb.int/report/mexico/hurricane-dean-ocha-situation-report-no-5 | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20140313030349/http://reliefweb.int/report/mexico/hurricane-dean-ocha-situation-report-no-5 | archivedate = 2014-03-13 | deadurl = no}}</ref>，海岸受到大浪的冲击<ref name="AFP_2007-08-19_jam" /><ref name="Hindi_08-19-07">{{cite web|author=AP Staff Writer |date=2007-08-19 |title=Tourists in Caribbean jam airports to escape Hurricane Dean |publisher=The Hindi |accessdate=2014-03-13 |archivedate=2012-10-26 |deadurl=yes |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20121026002621/http://www.hindu.com/thehindu/holnus/003200708190952.htm |url=http://www.hindu.com/thehindu/holnus/003200708190952.htm }}</ref>。大雨还在海地造成山体滑坡<ref name="Haiti_landslides">{{cite news | author = Chris Kraul | title = Mighty hurricane advances on Mexico | deadurl = no | url = http://www.smh.com.au/news/world/mighty-hurricane-rips-into-jamaica/2007/08/20/1187462176029.html | date = 2007-08-21 | accessdate = 2014-03-13 | publisher = Sydney Morning Herald | archivedate = 2012-10-23 | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20121023221037/http://www.smh.com.au/news/world/mighty-hurricane-rips-into-jamaica/2007/08/20/1187462176029.html}}</ref>，摧毁了成百上千的民房，迫使5154人住进临时避难所<ref name="reliefweb_2007-08-19_02" />，贝内特（{{lang|en|Bainet}}）都会区的供水系统也受到影响<ref name="OCHA_2007-08-24_01" />。

古巴、波多黎各和开曼群岛都经历大浪和暴雨，大开曼出现停电<ref name="reliferweb_paho_2007_08-20">{{cite web | author = Pan American Health Organization (PAHO) | publisher = Relief Web | date = 2007-08-20 | accessdate = 2014-03-13 | title = Hurricane Dean in the Caribbean: Situation Report 20 Aug 2007 | archivedate = 2014-03-13 | deadurl = no | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20140313075822/http://reliefweb.int/report/jamaica/hurricane-dean-caribbean-situation-report-20-aug-2007 | url = http://reliefweb.int/report/jamaica/hurricane-dean-caribbean-situation-report-20-aug-2007}}</ref>，但没有出现重大损失的报道<ref name="milenio_08_18" />，该岛有2000人于风暴来袭期间躲进临时避难所。飓风的外围雨带从8月19至21日掠过古巴，带去大雨和巨浪，但该国幸运地避过破坏性的狂风<ref name="reliferweb_paho_2007_08-20" />。波多黎各有多条道路因迪安产生的降水而被淹，该岛沿岸也出现大浪，但没有出现人员伤亡的报道<ref name="milenio_08_18" />。

=== 墨西哥 ===
[[File:Hurricane_Dean_landfall_AVN.jpg|thumb]]
迪安于2007年8月21日以五级飓风强度在金塔纳罗奥州的科斯塔玛雅地区小镇玛哈瓦附近登陆，之前其强度一直在增加<ref name="TCR" />。报告表明阵风时速高达320公里，不过该州旅游城市[[坎昆|坎昆]]和[[科苏梅尔岛|科苏梅尔]]都避开风暴最具破坏性的部分，然而，登陆点以南65公里的州首府[[切图马尔|切图马尔]]狂风肆虐，还爆发严重的洪灾<ref name="yahoo_2007-08-21_mex01">{{cite web |publisher=Yahoo! |author=Mark Stevenson (AP) |date=2007-08-21 |title=Category 5 Hurricane Dean slams Mexico |accessdate=2007-08-21 |deadurl=yes |archivedate=2007-08-21 |url=http://news.yahoo.com/s/ap/20070821/ap_on_re_la_am_ca/tropical_weather |archiveurl=https://www.webcitation.org/5RGSPIwrU?url=http://news.yahoo.com/s/ap/20070821/ap_on_re_la_am_ca/tropical_weather }}</ref>。拥有200人口的玛哈瓦镇完全被风暴摧毁。数百幢建筑物因[[风暴潮|风暴潮]]和强风而严重受损或彻底被毁<ref name="sfgate">{{cite news | archivedate = 2014-03-13 | deadurl = no | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20140313004244/http://www.sfgate.com/travel/article/Travelers-Checks-Hurricane-Dean-knocks-out-2544389.php | url = http://www.sfgate.com/travel/article/Travelers-Checks-Hurricane-Dean-knocks-out-2544389.php | title = Travelers' Checks: Hurricane Dean knocks out Costa Maya cruise port | publisher = San Francisco Chronicle | date = 2007-08-26 | accessdate = 2007-08-27 | author = Spud Hilton, John Flinn, Larry Habegger}}</ref>，连钢梁都被折弯<ref name="TCR" />。狂浪冲掉了科斯塔玛雅[[混凝土|混凝土]]邮轮港口的一部分，这里在之后近一年的时间里都无法向游船开放<ref name="sfgate" /><ref name="Fodors">{{cite web | url = http://www.fodors.com/news/story_2690.html | title = Hurricane Dean: Don't Cancel Your Trip | accessdate = 2014-03-13 | date = 2007-08-29 | publisher = Fordor's | author = Staff Writers | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20140312212739/http://www.fodors.com/news/story_2690.html | deadurl = yes | archivedate = 2014-03-12 }}</ref>。幸运的是，由于政府准备充足，气象部门预报及时而准确，这场风暴初次登陆时虽然力道巨大，但却没有造成任何人员丧生<ref name="scoop_aug_2007">{{cite web | author = United Nations | publisher = Scoop Independent News | date = 2007-08-22 | accessdate = 2014-03-13 | title = UN Teams Assessing Aftermath Of Hurricane Dean | url = http://www.scoop.co.nz/stories/WO0708/S00568.htm | archivedate = 2014-03-12 | deadurl = no | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20140312213604/http://www.scoop.co.nz/stories/WO0708/S00568.htm}}</ref><ref name="UN_applauds">
{{cite web | author = Diego Cevallos | publisher = Interpress Service | date = 2007-08-24 | accessdate = 2014-03-13 | title = Mexico: U.N. applauds nation for hurricane disaster prevention | via = HighBeam Research | url = http://www.highbeam.com/doc/1G1-167983680.html | archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20140611091103/http://www.highbeam.com/doc/1G1-167983680.html | archive-date = 2014-06-11 | dead-url = yes }}
</ref>。

8月22日，迪安在韦拉克鲁斯州东海岸小镇特科卢特拉附近实现二次登陆，[[伊达尔戈州|伊达尔戈州]]有两条山上的河流泛滥，当地向西直到太平洋海岸之间地区都出现降水。韦拉克鲁斯州州长菲德尔·埃雷拉（{{lang|es|Fidel Herrera}}）称该州遭受“数额极大的损失”<ref>{{cite news | url = http://travel.latimes.com/articles/la-tr-foreign26aug26 | title = Hurricane Dean's wake: updates from Mexico & the Caribbean | publisher = Los Angeles Times | date = 2007-08-23 | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20110930155248/http://travel.latimes.com/articles/la-tr-foreign26aug26 | accessdate = 2011-09-30 | author = Diana Dawson | deadurl = yes | archivedate = 2011-09-30}}</ref>，不过[[石油|石油]]生产没有受到严重影响并且很快就恢复正常<ref name="telegraph_mex_2007-08-24">{{cite web | author = Staff Writers | work = The Sunday Telegraph | date = 2007-08-24 | accessdate = 2014-03-13 | title = Hurricane Dean rains pound Mexico | archivedate = 2014-03-13 | deadurl = no | url = http://www.reuters.com/article/2007/08/24/us-storm-dean-idUSN2337533620070824 | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20140313092233/http://www.reuters.com/article/2007/08/24/us-storm-dean-idUSN2337533620070824}}</ref>。

